    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. The exterior has some cosmetic blemishes, and the interior surfaces show use. There may be minor mechanical items that need attention. No major structural or safety concerns, but buyers should expect a used vehicle that reflects its age and mileage.",
